<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
  Schema: Shape_composition_arm
   <express_ref linkend="shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm">
</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ Shape_element_constituent_relationship +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship">
	A <b>Shape_element_constituent_relationship</b> is a type of 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
	that associates a 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	with a second  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	to which the first  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	is a constituent. The  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	that is the constituent  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	is specified as the 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/>. 
	The  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	to which the constituent  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	is a constituent is specified as the 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/>. 
	A <b>Shape_element_constituent_relationship</b> may be a 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR1 -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship.wr:WR1">
	The  <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	that is specified as the 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/> 
	shall not be a constituent of itself, either directly or indirectly.
</ext_description>

<!-- WR2 -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship.wr:WR2">
	The
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relation_type"/>
	shall not be populated.
</ext_description>

<!-- UR1 -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship.ur:UR1">
	The combination of the 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/> inherited from  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
	and <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/> inherited from  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
	shall be unique within a population of 
	<b>Shape_element_constituent_relationship</b>. That is, any specific  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	shall not be a constituent of any one  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	more than once.
</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ Shape_element_composing_relationship +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship">
A <b>Shape_element_composing_relationship</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship"/> 
that associates a <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/> 
with a <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> from which the 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/> is composed.

</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship.relation_type">
a text value equal to 'composing'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship.relating">
an instance specifies the 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/> 
that is the <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
that is composed from the  
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
specified as the 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/> for the 
<b>Shape_element_composing_relationship</b>.
</ext_description>
<!-- +++++++++++ Composite_group_shape_element +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Composite_group_shape_element">

A <b>Composite_group_shape_element</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/> 
in which the composite may be thought of as a group of individual 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
in which any property that is applied to the <b>Composite_group_shape_element</b> is applied to each of the constituent 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s on an individual basis.
</ext_description>
<!-- +++++++++++ Composite_shape_element +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element">

A <b>Composite_shape_element</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
that is composed of two or more constituent 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s. A 
<b>Composite_shape_element</b> is either a 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_group_shape_element"/> or 
a <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_unit_shape_element"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element.composing_relationships">
an inverse relationship that specifies that the existence of the 
<b>Composite_shape_element</b> is dependent 
on the existence of the  
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship"/> 
that specifies the <b>Composite_shape_element</b> as its 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/>. 
There shall be 
two or more  <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship"/>
for a <b>Composite_shape_element</b>.
</ext_description>
<!-- +++++++++++ Composite_unit_shape_element +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Composite_unit_shape_element"><p>

A <b>Composite_unit_shape_element</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/> 
that is treated as a unit, as opposed to
as a group of individual 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>.


</p><example number="1">
A <express_ref linkend="Geometric_tolerance:arm:Geometric_tolerance_arm.Surface_profile_tolerance"/> 
is applied to a square cut-out that goes through a printed circuit board. The square cut-out is a 
<b>Composite_unit_shape_element</b> that consists of the four constituent 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s 
that correspond to the four surfaces of the cut-out.
</example>
<example number="2">
A <express_ref linkend="Geometric_tolerance:arm:Geometric_tolerance_arm.Flatness_tolerance"/> may be applied to a
<b>Composite_unit_shape_element</b> to specify that the coplanar surfaces that
make up the <b>Composite_unit_shape_element</b> are required to fall within a
common <express_ref linkend="Geometric_tolerance:arm:Geometric_tolerance_arm.Tolerance_zone"/>.
</example>


<note>
Common tolerance zones are described in 7.5 of ISO 1101.
</note>

</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ Shape_element_boundary_relationship +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_boundary_relationship">
<p>
	A <b>Shape_element_boundary_relationship</b> is a type of 
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
	that specifies that a <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> is the
	boundary or a portion of the boundary of another  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>. The
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/> 
	specifies the  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	that is the boundary or a portion of a boundary of the  
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
	specified as the
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/>.
</p>
	<note number="1">
		The attribute 
		<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/> 
		is declared in the
		<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
		entity of which this entity is a subtype.
	</note>
	<note number="2">
		The attribute 
		<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/>.
		is declared in the
		<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship"/> 
		entity of which this entity is a subtype.
	</note>
	<example>
		A <b>Shape_element_boundary_relationship</b> may be used to specify that a
		<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
		is one of the boundaries of a rectangular <express_ref linkend="Geometric_tolerance:arm:Geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum_target"/> 
		area. The boundary may then be located relative to a 
		<express_ref linkend="Geometric_tolerance:arm:Geometric_tolerance_arm.Datum"/> 
		with a 
		<express_ref linkend="Dimension_tolerance:arm:Dimension_tolerance_arm.Location_dimension"/>.
	</example>
</ext_description>

<!-- WR1 -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_boundary_relationship.wr:WR1">
	The
	<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relation_type"/>
	shall not be populated.
</ext_description>

<!-- +++++++++++ Shape_element_locating_relationship +++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship">
A <b>Shape_element_locating_relationship</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_composing_relationship"/> 
that is the association between two 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s in which the associated 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s are located in relation to each other. 
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship.located_shape_element">
specifies the <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
that is located in relation to the  
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
specified by the <b>locating_shape_element</b> for the <b>Shape_element_locating_relationship</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship.locating_shape_element">
specifies the 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
in relation to which the  
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/> 
specified by 
the <b>located_shape_element</b> is located for the <b>Shape_element_locating_relationship</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship.ur:UR1">
The combination of located and locating 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s 
shall be unique within a population of 
<b>Shape_element_locating_relationship</b>. That is, the same 
<express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>s 
shall not be located relative to each other more than once.
</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>

